function SndTest% SndTest alternately plays the same sound (someone saying "why") % with 8 or 16 bit encoding, to allow you the hear the difference, % which is a faint hiss produced by the coarse 8-bit quantization.% 1/8/00  Lu Lesmes, lesmes@usc.edu, wrote it.% 1/30/00 dgp cosmetic editing% 4/24/02 awi Exit on Win with message.% 5/30/02 awi Restore for Win.  Cosmetic.    [y,rate,bits]=wavread('SndTest.wav');for i=1:6% 	sound(y,FS,16)	Snd('Play',y',rate,16);	Snd('Wait');%	sound(y,FS,8)	Snd('Play',y',rate,8);	Snd('Wait');end